abstract: >-
  Live AI adversarial threat index. Attack success rates,
  defense efficacy, and compliance risk scores across
  foundation models, updated hourly. Sources include
  NVD/CVE, MITRE ATLAS, AI Incident Database, and
  OWASP LLM Top 10.
